  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>

    <para><para> </para>
<para> Receiver for Thread notifications</para>
<para></para>
<para> signal *, ORTD.DATATYPE_INT32 - The signal that was received</para>
<para> </para>
<para> This is a simulation-synchronising Block. Everytime a notification is received,</para>
<para> the simulation that contains this blocks goes on for one step.</para>
<para> </para>
<para> Notifications can be send from other threads by using ld_ThreadNotify</para>
<para> </para>
